Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:02.26,Cmt,,0,0,0,,注：戈休人（{\fnFOT-UDKakugo_Large Pr6N DB\fs48}ゴシュ人{\r}）和老公（{\fnFOT-UDKakugo_Large Pr6N DB\fs48}ご主人{\r}）发音相同
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.21,Furi,,0,90,0,,你老公
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.26,Furi,,0,540,0,,老公
